- Where he was the night that girl died.

37:02.720 --> 37:04.722
<i>- What girl?</i>
- The one in the park.

37:06.360 --> 37:08.362
<i>Did you lie?</i>

37:10.000 --> 37:12.002
Yes.

37:14.040 --> 37:17.362
<i>- Is this your one phone call?</i>
- Yes.

37:17.520 --> 37:21.081
<i>Sally... I 'm not a criminal solicitor.</i>

37:22.120 --> 37:26.648
<i>I should contact a colleague.
It's important you don't incriminate yourself</i>

37:26.800 --> 37:30.885
I'm pregnant, Steve. Please help me.

37:41.840 --> 37:43.842
Please remove your top layer, sir.

37:52.200 --> 37:54.202
Shoes.

38:28.120 --> 38:32.489
Both the Benedetto girl and Spector
have mobile devices with video files on them.

38:32.640 --> 38:34.961
