39:11.120 --> 39:14.442
I must advise you
this interview is being recorded.

39:16.040 --> 39:17.929
I am Detective Constable Glen Martin.

39:18.080 --> 39:20.560
Detective Constable
Gail McNally is also present.

39:20.720 --> 39:23.246
The suspect's name is Sally Ann Spector.

39:23.400 --> 39:26.961
Also present is the suspect's solicitor
Stephen Jennings.

39:27.840 --> 39:32.050
It is...2200 hours on Monday, May the 7th.

39:32.880 --> 39:36.566
This interview is taking place
in the Down Serious Crime Suite.

39:38.000 --> 39:42.927
I'd like each person here to identify themselves
on tape for voice identification purposes.

39:43.080 --> 39:44.969
DC Gail McNally.

39:45.520 --> 39:47.522
Steve Jennings, solicitor.

39:50.720 --> 39:52.722
Sally?

39:54.160 --> 39:56.401
Sally Ann Spector.

39:58.240 --> 40:00.208
Just to make it clear, Sally,

40:00.360 --> 40:05.082
<i>the offence you are being investigated for
is perverting the course of justice.</i>

40:05.960 --> 40:09.726
<i>What I am going to do is ask you
to give an account of the answers you gave me</i>

40:09.880 --> 40:13.930
<i>when I telephoned you
on Saturday the 21st of April,</i>

40:14.080 --> 40:17.846
<i>and asked you to give an account
of your husband Paul Spector's movements</i>

40:18.000 --> 40:20.128
<i>on a series of specific dates.</i>

40:20.720 --> 40:23.246
<i>I believe the account you gave me was false</i>

40:23.400 --> 40:26.449
<i>and amounted to an attempt
to pervert the course of justice.</i>

40:28.320 --> 40:30.527
<i>Do you understand?</i>

40:31.600 --> 40:33.602
<i>Yes.</i>

40:35.640 --> 40:39.042
<i>Tell me in your own words
how you came to give me that account.</i>

40:41.160 --> 40:42.889
<i>I lied.</i>

40:44.480 --> 40:46.482
<i>I lied to you.</i>

40:50.400 --> 40:54.325
Er.., He called me
before he went into the police station.

40:55.960 --> 40:59.089
He said the police
would probably come round to see me

40:59.240 --> 41:01.925
and ask me to confirm
what he was about to tell them.

41:05.000 --> 41:08.288
He asked me to lie
and say that I'd been with him that night.

41:10.800 --> 41:13.041
That we were at home together.

41:15.000 --> 41:17.128
What reason did he give, Sally?

41:18.120 --> 41:20.441
When he called he didn't give a reason.

41:20.600 --> 41:22.921
So you just did what he asked?

41:23.600 --> 41:24.931
Yes.

41:27.200 --> 41:29.089
Did he ever give a reason?

41:31.880 --> 41:35.407
Er...yes, when he came back from the station.

41:41.400 --> 41:43.402
Tell them, Sally.

41:51.400 --> 41:55.371
Paul worked on a suicide helpline,
as a volunteer.

41:57.240 --> 42:01.882
Every Friday night, all night,
and some other nights as well.

42:03.880 --> 42:06.167
Or at least that's where I thought he was.

42:08.800 --> 42:13.442
When he came back he told me that he hadn't
actually gone to work for the last three months.

42:15.440 --> 42:17.761
That he'd been having an affair.

42:24.000 --> 42:26.002
<i>Take your time.</i>

42:29.760 --> 42:34.641
<i>He was having an affair...with our baby-sitter.</i>

42:37.840 --> 42:39.410
<i>She was 15 at the time.</i>

42:41.120 --> 42:42.884
<i>I didn't know what to do.</i>

42:45.360 --> 42:49.729
