that he'd be put on the sex offenders list.

42:51.280 --> 42:55.888
That he'd go to prison.
That...I might even lose my job.

42:58.560 --> 43:00.881
Is that what all of this is about?

43:03.720 --> 43:06.803
You understand that you're under caution?

43:09.560 --> 43:16.967
I should also remind you...that you have a right
to free and independent legal advice.

43:20.800 --> 43:23.883
And that you can talk to a solicitor
on the telephone if you so wish.

43:27.800 --> 43:30.485
That light indicates
the interviews being monitored.

43:33.000 --> 43:39.281
You have been arrested because we believe
that on the night of Thursday, May the 3rd...

43:40.480 --> 43:43.370
...you abducted Rose Veronica Stagg
from her home.

43:45.520 --> 43:49.844
We also believe that you have
unlawfully imprisoned Rose Stagg.

43:51.400 --> 43:54.609
That you're holding her somewhere
against her will.

43:57.280 --> 44:00.170
You may know Rose Stagg better
as Rose McGill.

44:05.960 --> 44:08.247
Your wife has been arrested.

44:09.880 --> 44:12.087
Your home is being searched.

44:13.400 --> 44:15.641
Katie Benedetto has been arrested.

44:17.400 --> 44:20.609
The hotel room you were staying in
is being searched.

44:21.200 --> 44:26.684
Things could gel out of control
for you very quickly, Paul.

44:31.000 --> 44:33.924
<i>Are you sure you don't want to speak?</i>

44:36.200 --> 44:39.090
All the files have downloaded
from Spector's phone.

44:39.240 --> 44:41.402
There's some videos you should see.

44:46.320 --> 44:50.848
<i>My wrists are sore. Can you untie me, please?</i>

44:52.560 --> 44:56.451
<i>Peter? Can you unloosen these, please?</i>

45:02.040 --> 45:04.247
<i>I'm thirsty.</i>

45:05.640 --> 45:07.642
<i>Can you untie me, please!</i>

45:09.000 --> 45:12.083
<i>Please. Please can you untie me?</i>

45:14.320 --> 45:16.243
<i>Please take me home.</i>

45:16.440 --> 45:18.124
<i>Please take me home.</i>

45:18.280 --> 45:20.123
<i>My babies will be missing me.</i>

45:21.160 --> 45:23.083
<i>They're only little, they're young.</i>

45:23.240 --> 45:26.323
<i>They need me, Peter. They need me, Peter.</i>

45:36.000 --> 45:37.490
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

45:39.880 --> 45:43.930
<i>You were right. I did go to the police.</i>

45:44.960 --> 45:46.485
<i>...go to the police.</i>

