45:51.360 --> 45:53.647
<i>I won't tell anybody what's happened.</i>

45:54.200 --> 45:56.567
<i>Please, Peter.</i>

45:56.720 --> 45:59.007
<i>Please, Peter, would you talk to me?</i>

46:06.000 --> 46:08.162
<i>I miss what we had.</i>

46:08.320 --> 46:10.448
<i>Hm...I do.</i>

46:12.000 --> 46:14.002
<i>Tom...</i>

46:15.160 --> 46:17.401
<i>He's not like... you.</i>

46:17.560 --> 46:19.210
<i>You.</i>

46:19.360 --> 46:21.488
<i>No one's like you.</i>

46:23.520 --> 46:26.842
<i>Untie me and we can have what we had again.</i>

46:27.960 --> 46:30.167
<i>It can be better.</i>

46:30.760 --> 46:35.561
<i>I know it's wrong, but I'm...so turned on.</i>

46:37.400 --> 46:40.483
<i>Are you? Are you?</i>

46:43.200 --> 46:45.168
<i>Peter?</i>

46:47.680 --> 46:49.887
<i>You fucking disgust me!</i>

46:50.040 --> 46:52.168
<i>You fucking piece of shit!</i>

46:52.320 --> 46:53.924
<i>You fucking worm!</i>

46:54.080 --> 46:55.969
<i>I know it's you.</i>

46:56.240 --> 46:57.605
<i>You pervert.</i>

46:57.760 --> 47:00.764
<i>You fucking pervert!</i>

47:01.200 --> 47:04.010
<i>You dickless piece of shit.</i>

47:04.160 --> 47:07.289
<i>You're a monster. You're a monster.</i>

