<i>You're a monster. You're a fucking aberration!</i>

47:12.520 --> 47:14.204
<i>Fuck you! Fuck you!</i>

47:23.720 --> 47:26.610
<i>Peter, please take me home.</i>

47:41.440 --> 47:44.842
<i>You must have had a terrible childhood
