47:45.560 --> 47:48.211
<i>I feel sorry for you.</i>

47:49.160 --> 47:50.810
<i>I really do.</i>

47:50.960 --> 47:52.883
<i>You must have had a terrible childhood.</i>

47:53.040 --> 47:54.644
<i>I feel sorry for you.</i>

48:00.400 --> 48:03.688
<i>I don't want to die here, Peter, please!</i>

48:17.680 --> 48:20.081
<i>You want to be noticed?</i>

48:21.520 --> 48:25.161
<i>You want to be paid attention to,
