48:27.080 --> 48:29.606
<i>Fine. Hurt me.</i>

48:29.760 --> 48:31.762
<i>Do whatever you want to me.</i>

48:32.520 --> 48:35.888
<i>Go ahead...do your worst.</i>

48:36.040 --> 48:41.365
<i>Nothing you can do will ever take away
