48:57.720 --> 49:00.485
<i>Do you know that? Do you know that!</i>

49:07.320 --> 49:09.607
<i>Why the fuck are you watching this?</i>

49:10.880 --> 49:12.848
<i>You sick shit.</i>

49:13.560 --> 49:15.562
<i>What the fuck is wrong with you?</i>

49:44.760 --> 49:46.842
I think it's time for a special warning.

49:47.000 --> 49:49.526
See if we can't make it
that a court draws an adverse inference

49:49.680 --> 49:52.490
from Spector's refusal to answer questions.

49:52.640 --> 49:54.642
I'll pass it on.

50:17.720 --> 50:21.281
I want you to listen carefully
to what I'm about to say, Paul.

50:23.800 --> 50:26.531
I'm now going to ask you to account for a fact.

50:28.560 --> 50:30.722
The reason I'm asking you to do this...

50:33.000 --> 50:37.210
