of Rose Stagg.

50:46.840 --> 50:50.367
<i>I must warn you that a record
is being made of this interview...</i>

50:51.400 --> 50:54.688
<i>...and may be given in evidence
if you 're brought to trial.</i>

50:57.000 --> 51:00.402
