53:10.040 --> 53:12.486
- Give her my love.
- Granny!

53:12.640 --> 53:15.291
<i>I will. You try not to worry.</i>

53:18.120 --> 53:20.805
<i>Granny, is that Daddy on the phone?</i>

53:35.000 --> 53:37.651
- Gibson.
<i>- It's Christine Larkin, ma'am.</i>

53:37.800 --> 53:40.371
- Yes?
<i>- Some new results from the FSNI.</i>

53:41.200 --> 53:42.486
Tell me.

53:42.640 --> 53:44.608
<i>They've managed to type mitochondrial DNA</i>

53:44.760 --> 53:48.924
<i>from the degraded blood sample found on
the scissors that ties them to the crime scene.</i>

53:49.400 --> 53:51.402
<i>It's Joe Brawley's blood.</i>

53:54.080 --> 53:57.163
He's entitled to eight hours uninterrupted rest,
ma'am.

53:58.080 --> 54:02.404
If we wake him,
I have to reset the clock and you lose two hours.

54:08.440 --> 54:10.602
Fetch the gaoler.

54:28.720 --> 54:30.722
Yes, ma'am?

54:32.840 --> 54:34.842
May I?

54:46.520 --> 54:48.602
There's something I'd like you to do.

55:10.640 --> 55:13.041
I'm DC Gail McNally.

55:13.200 --> 55:17.649
Paul Spector, I'm further arresting you
for the murder of Joseph Brawley

55:17.800 --> 55:20.280
and the attempted murder of Anne Brawley.

55:20.440 --> 55:21.885
You do not have to say anything.

55:22.040 --> 55:24.691
But it may harm your defence
if you do not mention when questioned

55:24.840 --> 55:26.922
something you later rely on in court.

